業試驗所</organizationName><positionName>助理研究員</positionName><address scope="document"><deliveryPoint>台北市南海路53號</deliveryPoint><postalCode>10066</postalCode><country>台灣</country></address><phone phonetype="voice">00886-2-23039978#1613</phone><phone phonetype="fax">00886-2-23752164</phone><electronicMailAddress>chwang@tfri.gov.tw</electronicMailAddress></contact><methods><methodStep><description><section><title>樣區選定</title><para>1.竹種選擇：孟宗竹、麻竹</para><para>2.區域選擇：孟宗竹中、南部各一樣區；麻竹中、南部各一樣區。</para><para>3.樣株選取：1至5齡級各選5株。</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>試材採集</title><para>採集1至5年生之竹材，測定其高度與桿徑，並區分上、中、下三段分取試材。</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>比重與碳含量測定</title><para>1.比重測定：分別測量生材比重、絕乾比重及含水率。</para><para>2.碳含量測定：將竹材先研磨成小於100  mesh 篩網之細粒粉末後，取2~4mg 經絕乾後之試材粉末裝入儀器專用錫盒內，以元素分析儀 (Elementar Vario CHNS/O Analyzer, Elementar Analysensysteme, Hamburg, Germany) 測定樣品之碳含量組成百分比。</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>碳吸存轉換係數估算</title><para>計算各竹種、各齡級、各部位之碳吸存轉換係數，分析各竹種固定大氣中二氧化碳之能力。</para></section></description></methodStep></methods><access authSystem="knb" order="denyFirst" scope="document"><allow><principal>public</principal><permission>read</permission></allow></access><dataTable id="1185774969030" scope="document"><entityName>Results of Phyllostachys heterocycla</entityName><entityDescription>Revelant measured items for the bamboo species of Phyllostachys heterocycla.</entityDescription><physical scope="document"><objectName>~deleteme17258.tmp</objectName><dataFormat><textFormat><attributeOrientation>column</attributeOrientation><simpleDelimited><fieldDelimiter>#x09</fieldDelimiter></simpleDelimited></textFormat></dataFormat><distribution scope="document"><online><url function="download">ecogrid://knb/charcoal.31.1</url></online></distribution></physical><attributeList><attribute id="1185774969045" scope="document"><attributeName>Age</attributeName><at